TI  - Dose-dependent accumulation of glucose in the intestinal wall and lumen induced by metformin as revealed by 18F-labelled fluorodeoxyglucose positron emission tomography-MRI
PY  - 2021
T2  - Diabetes, Obesity and Metabolism
VL  - 23
IS  - 3
SP  - 692
